com.opentok.android

Class SubscriberKit.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opentok.android.SubscriberKit.Builder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Subscriber.Builder
    Enclosing class:
    SubscriberKit

    public static class SubscriberKit.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to build a SubscriberKit object. Instantiate a Builder object using the Builder(Context context, Stream stream) constructor. Then call methods of the Builder instance to add settings for the subscriber. Then call the build() method, which returns a SubscriberKit object.

    Use the Session.subscribe(SubscriberKit subscriber) method to start streaming video for the subscriber.
